# All env vars are OPTIONAL server-side fallbacks.
# Users can bring their own keys via the in-app Settings panel
# (stored in their browser's localStorage, sent with each request).
#
# Set any of these if you want the server to provide a default key
# when a visitor hasn't entered their own.

# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=AIza...

# Optional. Daily-per-IP rate limit (80 turns/day).
# Get free credentials at https://upstash.com/ (Redis -> REST API).
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=https://...
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=...
